==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|abductus||lang=la}}, perfect passive participle of {{term|abduco||to lead away|lang=la}}, from {{term|ab||away|lang=la}} + {{term|duco||to lead|lang=la}}<ref>{{R:CDOE|page=2}}</ref>.
* {{sense|physiology}} {{back-form|abduction}}.<ref>{{R:MW3 1976|page=3}}</ref>

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/æbˈdʌkt/|/æbˈdəkt/}}
* {{audio|En-us-abduct.ogg|Audio (US)}}
